08:47.460 --> 08:49.980
belongs to the whimsical world of cinema.

08:49.980 --> 08:52.580
Darth Vader's helmet from the Empire Strikes Back

08:52.580 --> 08:56.260
sold for just under $900,000 in 2019.

08:56.260 --> 08:58.420
Marilyn Monroe's iconic white dress

08:58.420 --> 09:01.780
