09:04.260 --> 09:07.100
by a movie star may be Dorothy's groovy slippers

09:07.100 --> 09:08.740
from The Wizard of Oz.

09:08.740 --> 09:11.700
The most recognizable symbol from the most beloved movie

09:11.700 --> 09:13.380
of the 20th century was listed

09:13.380 --> 09:16.380
